info.name: DIP server
info.description:
API for
- iOS app
- Web app

Config header:
- jsonerror: true -> return error as json format.
Example: 

{
  "status": 401,
  "code": "UNAUTHORIZED",
  "details": "Unauthorized"
}


If jsonerror false, return "UNAUTHORIZED".
- In request, add debug = 1 to watch error trace.
Example: {{API_URL}}/auth/fblogin?debug=1


P/S: Some APIs are not used in current version, so I skipped response example for them.
